<title>一线手机厂商，为何集体望向AI？</title>
<link>http://weixin.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&amp;query=%E8%99%8E%E5%97%85%E7%BD%91+%E4%B8%80%E7%BA%BF%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E5%8E%82%E5%95%86%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BA%E4%BD%95%E9%9B%86%E4%BD%93%E6%9C%9B%E5%90%91AI%EF%BC%9F</link>
